  <brief_title>Styrian Vitamin D Hypertension Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Styrian Vitamin D Hypertension Trial: A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled Trial to Evaluate the Effects of Vitamin D Supplementation on Systolic Ambulatory Blood Pressure in Vitamin D Deficient Hypertensive Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
